snippet.title: ComputerCraft 1.3 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Version 1.3 of ComputerCraft, the Minecraft mod that features in-game, programmable computers, now features programmable robotic turtles :)

Download and install from http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/892282-11-computercraft-13/
Join the computer club at http://www.computercraft.info

The music used in this video is "Living in the Future 2 (Instrumental)" by Akira the Don. Check out his music at http://www.akirathedon.com
